text: Actias philippinica is a moth in the family Saturniidae. It is found in the Philippines. It is very similar in appearance to Actias isis. ==Subspecies== * Actias philippinica philippinica Nässig & Treadaway, 1997 (Philippines: Luzon) * Actias philippinica bulosa Nässig & Treadaway, 1997 (Philippines: Palawan) ==References== Philippinica Category:Moths described in 1997 Category:Moths of Asia
title: Actias philippinica
